headline: GTA Online
subtitle: On the Podium This Week: Vapid Peyote Custom
content: Once you stumble out of your king-sized bed in the Penthouse, stop by the lobby of The Diamond Casino & Resort and give the Lucky Wheel a spin. This week, you could walk away with the keys to the Vapid Peyote Custom, an old-school lowrider and a carjacker's dream.
